Automate AWS ECS Service Restarts:
Setup a job to do nightly recycle of our ECS Services deployed in ECS Fargate Cluster.

Options available:
1. We can use Lamda & EventBridge services for automate.
2. AWS CLI = to achieve via Blue/Green Deployment experience.

Steps:
1. Create IAM Role & Policies >> 
2. Create EventBridge Rule(Schedule) >> 
3. Create Lamda function to update "Python Service-restart script(ecs_service_restart.py)" >> 
4. Add Lamda as "EventBridge Rule" as Target.
